description:
By the time Jacob and Austin get to their cabin, it’s dark, cold and wet. Luckily, the place is fully
loaded with a fireplace, cozy blankets, and some cocoa. The two guys will have to cuddle up
close to stay warm. And when this stepdad gets his hands on his boy, he can’t help but want to get
him fully loaded as well
title: Retreat at the Family Cabin RAW
